title: Command & Conquer 3 Tiberium Wars NTSC/U Xbox 360
description:
Command & Conquer 3 Tiberium Wars:

Region      : NTSC/U                Languages: English        
Size        : 1 DVD                 Genre    : Strategy/Sim         
Platform    : XBOX 360              Date     : 05/2007

About:

The year is 2047 and Tiberium, a mutagenic green crystal, has infested planet Earth and divided it into three zones. Blue is the last refuge of the civilized world, Yellow is war-torn and ridden with disease, and the Red Zone is nothing but a wasteland. Live-action video clips combine seamlessly with more than 30 single-player missions for a sweeping story. The power of technology is displayed as you blow chunks off enemy tanks with your rockets. Fog of war takes on new meaning as smoke, fire, haze, tracers, explosions, and state-of-the-art weather effects all contaminate the battlefield. Combine units to create super-units and wipe your enemies off the face of the planet!
